        <h2><strong>Welcome, h.</strong></h2>
        <p>
          You, Marcos David Acosta, probably have a few questions (if not, you should).
          First, why am I addressing you like I would an audience?
          Second, why didn't you have to solve an incredibly elaborate and well-crafted puzzle to get to this page?
          And, third, why am I sending this to you on a day that is verifiably not your birthday?
        </p>
