          You see, this is no ordinary Marcos birthday present.
          I have gone through the incredible effort of making sure that this birthday spectacular is one for the ages.
          Unbenknownst to you (the world's worst detective, literally), during the course of the past three months* I have crafted the most elaborate present of your life, which is slated to start on June 1, 2023.
